# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

---

## [Unreleased]

### Added

### Changed

### Fixed

---

## [1.0.6] - 2026-04-09

### Changed

* Updated HMC version to **3.4.2** in `setup_fp_system_app_hmc.sh` (from `hmc-lib` package)

### Added

* Added comments to verify download of HMC tar package from GitHub repository

---

## [1.0.5] - 2025-11-14

### Changed

* Updated HMC version to **3.3.0** in `setup_fp_system_app_hmc.sh` (from `hmc-lib` package)

---

## [1.0.4] - 2023-08-18

### Changed

* Updated NCO from **4.8.0** to **5.1.7** in `setup_fp_system_app_nco.sh`
* Configured `antlr` and `udunits2` libraries to be compiled from source instead of system repositories

### Fixed

* Ensured commands in all bash scripts are set in root path instead of binaries path

---

## [1.0.3] - 2023-08-04

### Added

* Added `--enable-ncap2` flag to build the `ncap` binary in `setup_fp_system_app_nco.sh`

---

## [1.0.2] - 2023-05-18

### Added

* Added script for installing CDO application in `setup_fp_system_app_nco.sh`

---

## [1.0.1] - 2023-03-03

### Changed

* Updated HMC version to **3.1.6** in `setup_fp_system_app_hmc.sh` (from `hmc-lib` package)

---

## [1.0.0] - 2022-05-23

### Added

* Added script for installing HMC application in `setup_fp_system_app_hmc.sh` (version **1.7.1** from `fp-envs` package)
* Added script for installing CDO application in `setup_fp_system_app_cdo.sh`

---

